'''Option键'''是[[苹果标准键盘|苹果标准键盘]]中的按键，一般位于[[Control键|Control键]]与[[Command键|Command键]]之间。现代的[[蘋果公司|苹果]]台式机和笔记本的键盘上有两个Option键，分别位于[[空格键|空格键]]两侧。

苹果通常使用 ⌥（U+2325）来代表Option键。<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.fileformat.info/info/unicode/char/2325/index.htm|title = Unicode Character 'OPTION KEY' (U+2325)|accessdate = 2015-08-23|author = |date = |publisher = |language = en|archive-date = 2015-08-26|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150826154914/http://www.fileformat.info/info/unicode/char/2325/index.htm|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.macuknow.com/node/3660|title = 淺談 option 鍵 ⌥ {{!}} MacUknow|accessdate = 2015-08-23|author = Gary|date = 2010-08-03|publisher = |archive-date = 2015-04-15|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150415102244/http://macuknow.com/node/3660|dead-url = no}}</ref>

从20世纪90年代开始，[[Mac電腦|苹果电脑]]的Option键上也有“[[转换键|Alt]]”字样<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.computerhope.com/jargon/o/optionkey.htm|title = What is option key?|accessdate = 2015-08-23|author = |date = |publisher = Computer Hope|language = en|archive-date = 2015-07-30|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150730070203/http://www.computerhope.com/jargon/o/optionkey.htm|dead-url = no}}</ref>，但实现的功能与[[类Unix系统|类Unix系统]]或[[Microsoft_Windows|Windows系统]]的Alt键不同。特别要注意它不是用来访问菜单或快捷键，而是用作其他命令代码的修饰键，也有助于访问[[附加符号|附加符号]]。从这个角度说它类似[[IBM_PC兼容机|IBM PC兼容机]]键盘上的[[AltGr键|AltGr键]]。

